{"tid":84311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鄰國奇聞】“治不好污水就去喝河水”　 這位官員真的喝了","createTime":"2017-01-17T12:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T02:59:50.000Z","uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43446eb7ea0cb5f49224932d0418ee8a0094afc4","tid":84311,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"據澎湃新聞網報道，2016年5月，浙江省麗水市經濟技術開發區管委會丁紹雄公開表態，如果龍石溪消除不了劣五類，他將趴下去喝水！<br />\n<br />\n2016年12月29日，記者跟隨丁紹雄等人，再次來到龍石溪，沿著龍石溪水質改造工程從上游走到下游，查看水質情況。在記者面前，丁紹雄竟用雙手捧起溪水往嘴裡送。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KPIKRqM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKPIKRqM.jpg&h=242dfe52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c48639386a7f4d58b2c5e827c7ad5d70e098dc4","tid":84311,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"記者迅速采樣，送至檢測機構檢測。經麗水環境監測中心檢測，2016年12月29日採集的水樣結果為：氨氮：1.21mg/L，總磷：0.087mg/L，高錳酸鹽指數：1.70mg/L，這些鮮活的數據表明，龍石溪確實消除了劣五類的標準了。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Zg20jEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZg20jEU.jpg&h=8ae641fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd739a0afdf226f31795cd0a06cf9d6d05e650ae","tid":84311,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pPVZCc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpPVZCc5.jpg&h=e4d8e289&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61d79f9e623f45d035934f8caca8fecc1ca220f5","tid":84311,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"傻仔都知佢無飲落肚"},{"pid":"e0a7f73305fae84bf30e0a02c45f73e9c1dbef69","tid":84311,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:28:20.000Z","msg":"從2016年7月開始，龍石溪沿線100米範圍內的73家企業紛紛破土整改，企業內的雨水管一律明溝明渠，污水管也架空鋪設，為污水處理池打上&ldquo;補丁&rdquo;，並進行閉水試驗，絕不讓一滴污水流入龍石溪。<br />\n<br />\n同時，開發區邀請企業管理者一起8次下河清淤，讓他們感受到企業排出來的污水到底有多髒多臭，從而增強環保意識。 (來自:澎湃新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/JA1Yt91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJA1Yt91.jpg&h=d899bc2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb809d53486ead12a66efbef2cb9aab93ec0438d","tid":84311,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:29:20.000Z","msg":"濕濕嘴"},{"pid":"790cbd4f111d1a5fef55bf42451016594b8a057c","tid":84311,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記者迅速采樣，送至檢測機構檢測。經麗水環境監測中心檢測，2016年12月29日採集的水樣結果為：氨氮：1.21mg/L，總磷：0.087mg/L，高錳酸鹽指數：1.70mg/L，這些鮮活的數據表明，龍石溪確實消除了劣五類的標準了。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Zg20jEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZg20jEU.jpg&h=8ae641fe&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面個支豉油嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222860d38b2b174dc60a1a5659b0a18dda34475a","tid":84311,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>記者迅速采樣，送至檢測機構檢測。經麗水環境監測中心檢測，2016年12月29日採集的水樣結果為：氨氮：1.21mg/L，總磷：0.087mg/L，高錳酸鹽指數：1.70mg/L，這些鮮活的數據表明，龍石溪確實消除了劣五類的標準了。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Zg20jEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZg20jEU.jpg&h=8ae641fe&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面個支豉油嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cd2571c7b6f47022648ef9ca8329ff07f67bc8","tid":84311,"uid":16554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockq